                <h2> Caridad Center is the largest free clinic in Florida</h2>
                <p class="missionstatement"> Caridad Center's mission and vision is to upgrade the health, education, and living standards of underserved children and families; and to eliminate the cycle of poverty for the families we serve in South Florida.</p>

                <h2>CARIDAD CENTER OFFERING COVID-19 VACCINE </h2>

                <p>Caridad Center is partnering with the Palm Beach County Health Department to provide COVID-19 vaccines at the Caridad Center every Thursday, from 9:00 am – 12:00 pm by appointment only. Call now to make an appointment: <a href="tel:+561-600-1675" >561-600-1675</a></p>

                <p> The Pfizer and Moderna vaccines are provided by the Department of Health (DOH).  The vaccination shots will be administered to anyone eligible.  For more information about the vaccination program or to make an appointment please call the Caridad Center Vaccine Hotline at <a href="tel:+561-600-1675" >561-600-1675</a>.</p>
